summary: 该插件用于检测Metabase是否存在未授权命令执行漏洞（CVE-2023-38646），通过构造特定payload触发DNSLog验证漏洞存在性。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether Metabase has an unauthenticated command execution vulnerability (CVE-2023-38646) by constructing a specific payload and triggering DNSLog to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
